# Summary
This documentation page describes the Amplitude to Statsig event streaming integration, which allows sending Amplitude events to Statsig for feature management and experimentation. It covers setup requirements including obtaining a Statsig Server Secret Key, configuration steps in Amplitude, and important considerations like user ID matching and event size limitations.

